# SCSS

- Use `@use` / `@forward` — never `@import`
- Tokens: `@use '$scss/var/tokens' as *`
- Mixins: `@use '$scss/var/mixins' as *` then `@include mixin-name`
- Component styles stay in scoped `<style lang="scss">` blocks
- Run `npm run lint:css` — no Prettier
